precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-283 that provides for the
reimbursement of actual and reasonable travel expenses incurred by the
Chairperson and Commissioners of the CANADIAN TRANSPORTATION ACCIDENT
INVESTIGATION AND SAFETY BOARD ACT REVIEW COMMISSION while travelling
outside Canada.
